OL,3,CMan, 78, in court charged with woman's
OL,4,Cmurder
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fwith murder following the death of a
OL,8,F77-year-old woman, police say.
OL,10,FMichael Wall, 78, of Hillcrest Avenue,
OL,11,FStockton, Teesside, appeared at
OL,12,FTeesside Magistrates' Court on
OL,13,FWednesday 18 March, Cleveland Police
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe force said officers were called to
OL,17,Fa property in Hillcrest Avenue around
OL,18,F1am on Sunday where the woman was
OL,19,Ffound dead.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/2
